-- ==========================================
-- AUTO PLACE UNIT V6 (Game-Restart Aware)
-- ==========================================
-- Fix dari V5 (priority tidak reset setelah game restart):
--
--   ROOT CAUSE V5:
--     - prioritySatisfied[i] hanya di-init sekali saat script load.
--     - Setelah game restart (via AutoReplay), script tetap hidup di
--       executor, prioritySatisfied[1..2] = true dari game sebelumnya.
--     - Akibatnya hasPendingPriority() = false, priority phase di-skip,
--       AWAL slots tidak di-place di game baru.
--
--   FIX V6:
--     a) Auto-detect game restart via WAVE TURUN
--        (lastWaveNum >= 2 dan currentWave < lastWaveNum -> restart).
--     b) Auto-detect via WAVE CYCLE (wave naik dari >= STOP_WAVE,
--        lalu turun ke <= START_WAVE -> restart).
--     c) Saat restart terdeteksi, RESET semua state:
--        - prioritySatisfied[i]   -> false
--        - priorityAttempts[i]    -> 0
--        - mainSatisfied[i]       -> false
--        - refill main & backup bag
--        - cumulative stats tetap (agar user bisa lihat total semua game)
--     d) Main loop pakai SINGLE STATE MACHINE
--        (priority -> main, bisa kembali ke priority kalau reset).
--     e) Manual RESET button di GUI (kalau auto-detect missed).
--     f) GUI menampilkan game count ("Game #2") dan timestamp reset.
--     g) Boot delay setelah reset (RESET_COOLDOWN) supaya server siap.
-- ==========================================

